attributes.name: Vuber 510 Wax Adapter (N/A Pulse Touch)
attributes.body:
The Pulse Wax Adapter is the perfect accessory for any Pulse user. It easily attaches to your favorite wax atomizer or Vuber Atlas Top, allowing you to vape with a wide range of devices. The Pulse Wax Adapter is the perfect accessory for any Pulse user. Simply screw your favorite atomizer/mouthpiece into the Pulse and you're ready to go!


(*works with most wax atomizer/mouthpiece combinations)

attributes.name: Vuber 510 Magnetic Adapter (N/A Pulse Touch)
attributes.body:
The Pulse Magnetic Adapter allows you to use your favorite magnetic cartridge with the Pulse. This makes it easy for you to switch between different cartridges, allowing for optimal versatility and convenience. The Pulse Magnetic Adapter works with most magnetic cartridges, so there's no need to choose just one type. Whether you prefer a disposable or reusable cartridge, the Pulse Magnetic Adapter works with most magnetic cartridges.


(*works with most magnetic cartridges)

attributes.name: Vuber Atlas Atomizer
attributes.body:
The Atlas Vape Atomizer replacement atomizers are designed for the ultimate in discreet vaping, stainless steel construction keeps your pen cool while the dual-coil titanium heating elements & quartz cores ensure that your vapor is thick and flavorful. It comes with a deep bowl, optimally holding .4 grams of your favorite solid concentrate.

RECOMMENDED USE: Solid Concentrates: waxes, shatters, crumbles, resins, etc.

attributes.name: Vuber Suction Cup Small
attributes.body:
Have you ever lost your Vuber Battery? This is the solution. Keep all of your Vuber Batteries, Pencils, and Pens organized while they charge! The Suction Cup Pen Holder is perfect for holding your Favorite Vuber Battery upright so you know where it is. The silicone suction cup will adhere to most clean, flat surfaces, letting you show off your Vuber wherever you like.


Battery Fit Guide:

Small-Pilot, Solo, Comet, Pulse Touch
